        if EnableCastCurse = 1 and timer CurseTimer > 60000 and mana >= 11 and diffhits < ActivateAutoHealHPdiff and not dead ClosestTarget and find ClosestTarget ground -1 -1 TargetAttackRange and findtype 3972 self and findtype 3976 self and findtype 3980 self
            clearsysmsg 
            cast 'Curse'
            settimer spellTimer 0
            settimer AntiStallTimer 0
            @setvar! SpellcastCooldown 800

            while not targetexists and timer AntiStallTimer < 2500
                if diffhits >= ActivateAutoHealHPdiff
                    interrupt
                    @setvar! AttackModeActive 1
                    @setvar! CastingWasInterrupted 1
                    break
                endif

                if dead ClosestTarget or not find ClosestTarget ground -1 -1 TargetAttackRange
                    @setvar! RepeatCastingPoison 0
                    @setvar! AttackModeActive 0
                    @setvar! CastingWasInterrupted 1
                    @setvar! ClosestTargetisSticky 0
                    @setvar! TargetSwap 0
                    interrupt
                    break
                endif

                if insysmsg "Your concentration is disturbed"
                    interrupt
                    @setvar! CastingWasInterrupted 1
                    break
                endif

                if timer AntiStallTimer > 2500
                    settimer AntiStallTimer 0
                    break
                endif

                if timer spellTimer < SpellcastCooldown
